title: Bikerumor Pic Of The Day: Dangast, Germany
content:
Photo submitted by Jens, “The first nice spring day in Northern Germany. A tour on my 1955 Göricke, equipped with Carradice old school bikepacking gear. The view from Dangast over the Jade Bay towards Wilhelmshaven.” We always love seeing photos from where you are riding and are happy to share them with our readers around the world here […]
